2 PDN
3 NPD
4 NDP
5 DPN
6 DNP

Whereas *flipping* gives 8 possibilities.

   P  N  D
  -- -- --
1  H  H  H
2  H  H  T
3  H  T  H
4  H  T  T
5  T  H  H
6  T  H  T
7  T  T  H
8  T  T  T

Nice try.

