Manawahe (pop 0 )
One small hall at junction of 3 narrow, single lane roads.
Used about twice a year.

Te Mahoe (pop 1)
Small village nestled at the base of  the Matahina dam.
One school (primary only.)

Te Teko (pop 2)
Small town on a state highway. 
